video_title: DISCIPLINE can change your life ENTIRELY  #adviceoftheday #podcast #mindsetpodcast
transcript:
you don't need discipline to go and have
that glass of wine you don't need
discipline to eat that ice cream to try
to numb your feelings you need
discipline to do all of the opposite of
those things to say no to the glass of
wine to say no to the ice cream say no
to sleeping in because you love yourself
so much and you're not going to deal
with the anymore and you're GNA
push yourself to be better
